metadata.name: Future
metadata.description:
The future ahead seems exciting and full of infinite possibilities. As we advance in space exploration, we are discovering new planets and stars in our universe every day. With the development of more advanced technologies, such as space telescopes and space probes, we are learning more about galaxies and nearby star systems. This knowledge will provide us with a deeper understanding of the evolution of the universe and life in space, which in turn will allow us to advance in the exploration and colonization of other habitable planets. With new ways to travel through space, it is possible that one day we may see humanity establish colonies on distant planets, opening up new frontiers and opportunities for our species.

Technique: Procreate + Photoshop
Size: 2480x3508px, 300dpi
